{"tid":368393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暑假才過一半　17歲高中妹為iPhone7援交 每次3500元台幣","createTime":"2017-08-21T13:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T06:46:42.000Z","uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"366b7f38ab1c7dc923e2742130ce110ea0aa7595","tid":368393,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:39:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170813/1181259/%E6%9A%91%E5%81%87%E6%89%8D%E9%81%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E3%80%80%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%84%9B%E7%98%8B7%EF%BC%81%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%A6%B9%E6%8F%B4%E4%BA%A430%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flocal%2F20170813%2F1181259%2F%25E6%259A%2591%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%2589%258D%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258D%258A%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BA%2586%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%2598%258B7%25EF%25BC%2581%25E9%25AB%2598%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E6%258F%25B4%25E4%25BA%25A430%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=ZXOFqNCCuWIl91%2F%2FYo6SXmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ad28bcd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170813/1181259/%E6%9A%91%E5%81%87%E6%89%8D%E9%81%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E3%80%80%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%84%9B%E7%98%8B7%EF%BC%81%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%A6%B9%E6%8F%B4%E4%BA%A430%E4%BA%BA</a><br />\n暑假過了一個多月，1名高中女生為買手機，下海援交賺進約10萬元。<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，台南1名17歲女高中生為買iPhone 7，趁暑假利用手機交友APP「BeeTalk」、「SayHi」及「WeChat」等通訊軟體拉客，暑假一個半月，她援交近30人，每次3500元，估收入約10萬元。<br />\n警方網路巡邏查獲該名高中生與男客性交易，根據對話紀錄傳喚男客到案說明，與未滿18歲青少年性交易，最高可處3年以下有期徒刑，全案依違反兒童及少年性剝削防制條例偵辦。​（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"a817ae22dadb55511ec55495f72481488e5a9602","tid":368393,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"3500台幣咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6955744374959ffb24ecadb635d65ab3b0889f","tid":368393,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}